  "texts": [
    "Our few-shot models are also robust as measured by standard deviation.",
    "Null prompts exhibit comparable results with no significant difference in performance, especially with few-shot sizes exceeding 100.",
    "Contextualize data with surrounding context paragraphs improved classification results for most section classes, especially primary classes.",
    "It allowed our base models to correctly predict our running false-positive sample as Zusammenfassung.",
    "However, compared to the base models interpretability analysis using SHAP revealed that the large model places greater emphasis on main paragraph tokens rather than on context paragraphs."
